	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Mages two strongest fields are Evo and Conj, so if you happen to have a few ability points left over, and want to dump a few into casting, try and choose div, alt, or abj, as they dont get used as much and dont go up in skill as fast.<br><br>Graccil da Gnomie<br>51st Elementalist<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
